{
  "stem": "11723.2",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.9,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "My father had a passport.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "He couldn't get a visa.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "My grandparents, nobody.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "Nobody wanted us.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "And after a while, Jews had to move into certain sections of the city.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 30,
      "text": "And my parents, I believe, decided that we don't want to be identified with the rest of the population.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 4,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 31,
      "text": "We don't want to be taken into houses where only Jews live.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So for a great deal of money, they bought false papers.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But they were really good false papers.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I mean, I don't know what offices did it for them, but it was really official stuff and everybody had false papers.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 5,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Under what name?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 6,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I was Agnes Kovacs.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "K-O-V-A, with an accent, C-S.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "It means Smith in Hungarian.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And it's just about as common a name as Smith in English.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So I was Agnes Kovacs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And I was supposed to have been Protestant.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And my sister, who was 2 and 1/2-- not quite, not quite, she wasn't quite 2 yet-- she was called Susanna Kovacs.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And my father had a friend called Regeur Slani, who was a real righteous Christian.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "He was-- and I definitely want to talk about him, because he was unique in that country of evil people.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "I guess he went to university with my father, but he was older.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And he was a retired colonel in the Hungarian army.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "So he could don his uniform any time and walk freely the streets at any time during the, even during the raids and war and any time.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And so after we had the papers, what happened was that my father was going to be hiding out in Mr.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Slani's apartment.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Mr.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "Slani, who lived in [NON-ENGLISH] Street-- this I remember.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "I don't remember the street I was at, but I remember Mr.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 7,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "Slani.",
      "word_count": 1
    }
  ],
